<div id="content" class="components">
<div class="title">Content Commons</div>
<p>
Connexions provides the means for all kinds of authors both to 
contribute to an open &#147;Commons&#148; of information and to 
collaborate with each other.
</p>
</div>

<div id="software" class="components">
<div class="title">Software</div>
<p>
Connexions has developed an array of new and scalable software to 
facilitate the ways content is encoded, stored, retrieved, viewed, 
marked, taught, and edited.
</p>
</div>

<div id="vision" class="components">
<div class="title">Our Vision</div>
<p>
We intend to take Connexions to a critical mass on a global scale and
have the means to make this possible.
</p>
</div>

<div id="ip" class="components">
<div class="title">Intellectual Property</div>
<p>
Both the content and software of Connexions are provided under open
licenses that provide for free use, but are also fair, responsible, and
legally sound.
</p>
</div>

<div id="quality" class="components">
<div class="title">Quality</div>
<p>
The fast-paced development of content in our Commons lends itself to 
post-publication review, accomplished via Lenses through which the 
Modules are viewed.
</p>
</div>

<div id="connexions" class="components">
<div class="title">Working Together</div>
<p>
Our free and open Content, array of open-source Software, Vision for
growth, fair Intellectual Property practices, and Quality assurance are
the intertwined aspects that drive all our work.
</p>
</div>

